Connection management:

[x] when guest joins a room entry, it trys to establish a TCP connection to the host

[] once connected
	[] guest start sending periodical heartbeat(through the TCP connection) to host to indicate its signal strength
	[] host still sends periodical UDP broadcast to indicate its signal strength to all guests
	[] host send guest list to the newly connected guest so they can initialize their room UI

[] in the room
	[] when host finds a new guest has joined the room, it tells all guests(through the TCP connection) about it so they can update their room UI
	[] when a guest exits the room, it tells the host(TCP), then disconnect
	[] when host finds a guest has exited, it tells all guests(TCP) about it so they can update their room UI

